name: Ode to The Master
description: Ode to Ednaldo Pereira and his iconic song Vale Nada Vale Tudo. One of my favorite living legends coming from Guarabira, Brazil, Ednaldo is a real honest, kind and loving human being in a crazy crazy world. Inspiration is the key-word, grattitude is the feeling.  "Worth nothing Worth everything" as the master sings...  4200x1400 png
